<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Jan1934"><font color="red">1 January 1934</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): I wrote to you at the beginning of last month with regard to the cover design for The Mime &hellip; May I, please, hear from you with regard to this? </div>
